---
const quick = [
  "Offline-first, zero-trust camera network isolation",
  "Secure stream gateway + encrypted restream",
  "AI adapter ecosystem (community + verified)",
  "Auditability: logs, retention, exports",
];
---
<section style="padding: 54px 0 18px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="badge">
      <span style="width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:999px; background: var(--ok);"></span>
      Community Edition is free & open source
      <span class="kbd">Apache-2.0</span>
    </div>

    <h1 style="margin: 16px 0 10px; font-size: clamp(34px, 4vw, 56px); line-height:1.05;">
      Open-source NVR built for <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2)); -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color: transparent;">security</span> and <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand2), var(--brand)); -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color: transparent;">controlled AI</span>.
    </h1>

    <p style="margin:0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 18px; line-height:1.6; max-width: 880px;">
      OpenNVR isolates cameras on a private network, gates access through a secure stream layer, and enables an AI adapter ecosystem with governance and auditabilityâ€”ideal for regulated and offline-first deployments.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn primary" href="/downloads">Get started</a>
      <a class="btn" href="https://docs.opennvr.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read docs</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/security">Threat model</a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-grid">
      {quick.map((q) => (
        <div class="card" style="padding: 14px 14px;">
          <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;">
            <div style="width:10px; height:10px; border-radius:4px; margin-top:6px; background: rgba(125,211,252,.75);"></div>
            <div style="color: var(--muted); line-height:1.5;">{q}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 18px;
  }

  .hero-cta .btn {
    min-height: 44px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 22px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .hero-cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
